briefDescription: Organization is like a human being, undergoes lifecycle changes, from infant to child, moving up as a teenager and developing into a mature adult. Over a decade of its existence, it has expanded its services into several spheres of the developmental activities to achieve its vision of sustainable development on a larger scale.
